00:42:15.005 --> 00:42:18.465
purely real number.
So, this whole thing could be

00:42:18.465 --> 00:42:21.385
36, for example.
Well, we know how to divide the

00:42:21.385 --> 00:42:22.690
numerator by 36,
right?

00:42:22.690 --> 00:42:24.970
x_1x_2 +
y_1y_2

00:42:24.970 --> 00:42:27.310
some number, maybe 9;
then you divide by 36.

00:42:27.310 --> 00:42:30.440
One-fourth.
This could be i times 18.

00:42:30.440 --> 00:42:33.260
It would be 36,
